    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《METAL EDEN》</strong>是一款惊险刺激的科幻第一人称射击游戏。<br>先进的<strong>HYPER UNIT ASKA</strong>被派去执行自杀式任务，要从巨型独立都市<strong>Moebius</strong>中拯救市民的<strong>核心</strong>。这座都市曾是人类充满希望的新家园，现在却变成了致命的陷阱。<br>在网络战争中冲破<strong>内卫部队</strong>的防御，与<strong>工程师</strong>对抗，揭开<strong>EDEN</strong>计划的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/c920c1040fc353127a2645752403e7e7.webp?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/00a374874903cd338af069f473af57a1.poster.avif?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/00a374874903cd338af069f473af57a1.webm?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/00a374874903cd338af069f473af57a1.mp4?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入网络战争，对抗旨在保护一个人造世界的秘密机械力量。与各种强悍、敏捷的机甲部队和元素军队战斗。提取能量核心并摧毁<strong>内卫部队</strong>的护盾，以获得战区优势。发展你的武器库和战斗能力，成为势不可挡的<strong>HYPER UNIT</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/8f8937e12f58e43b350b055842ca1a66.poster.avif?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/8f8937e12f58e43b350b055842ca1a66.webm?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/8f8937e12f58e43b350b055842ca1a66.mp4?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个<strong>HYPER UNIT</strong>，也就是先进的战斗机器人。<br>你是专为保护他人而制造的。你擅长侦察任务，由<strong>幻影核心</strong>驱动。你可以使用增强的跑酷技能，运用冲刺、抓钩和沿墙奔跑突破<strong>内卫部队</strong>的防线。在令人心跳加速的遭遇战中，发挥你卓越的敏捷性和杂技般的战斗能力。化身为<strong>装甲冲撞球</strong>冲锋陷阵，对抗新的致命机器敌人。利用重力钩和喷气背包控制飞行并主宰战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/5fd223a56b7246c1a328d87918a5d206.webp?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/bffe3c0e040bc76aa65dbbe4377070b5.poster.avif?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/bffe3c0e040bc76aa65dbbe4377070b5.webm?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/bffe3c0e040bc76aa65dbbe4377070b5.mp4?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MOEBIUS</strong>是一座高耸于星球表面的巨型独立都市，守护着神秘的<strong>蜂巢塔</strong>。这座城市由神秘的<strong>工程师</strong>管理，曾经是人类充满希望的新家园，如今却变成了致命的陷阱。探索这座废弃轨道都市残破的粗犷环境，以及下方的神秘世界<strong>VULCAN</strong>。扮演<strong>HYPER UNIT ASKA</strong>，参与一场持续不断的冲突，争夺储存在加固存储单元中的人类殖民地的意识。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/5bb1ceabe553e0eeab0251464d9088cc.poster.avif?t=1760540216\" width=606 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/5bb1ceabe553e0eeab0251464d9088cc.webm?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/990380/extras/5bb1ceabe553e0eeab0251464d9088cc.mp4?t=1760540216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
